item.description: Please join us for a FREE introduction to EFT (Emotional Freedom Techniques™), the revolutionary healing method that targets unresolved emotional issues and the potential blocks to vibrant love, health and prosperity! The workshop itself is worth 6 CONTACT HOURS for NURSES/ LNA  in NH and MA and will be facilitated by Approved EFT Practitioner and Teacher, Susan Nordemo, RN, a speaker and workshop presenter with 20 years experience in the healing arts. Sue brings passion, humor and compassion to her audience and you will be sure to have a great time!

group.name: Abundance, Empowerment and the Law of Attraction

item.name: Intro to Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT) with Sue Nordemo
